<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Doctor Verification</title>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Hello Doctor! To join our community, you need to verify. For this, please provide the following details:</p>

    <form action="/doc" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <label for="images">Upload Images:</label>
        <input type="file" id="images" name="doqment" ><br>

        <label for="name">Your Name:</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required><br>

        <label for="username">Your email:</label>
        <input type="email" id="username" name="username" required><br>

        <button type="submit">Verify and Join</button>
    </form>

    <p>Already verified? <a href="/docSignup">Click here</a> to join our community.</p>
</body>
